</emphasis>
The species name is a Latin adjective (
<emphasis box="[775,1038,1878,1901]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="20">corniger, -gera, -gerum</emphasis>
= bearing horns).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
